Title: Giovanna Signature Womens Washable 2-piece Peplum Embellished Skirt Suit
Description:
Make a statement at the office with this Giovanna Signature women's peplum skirt suit. Show off the top half of this two-piece set, which consists of a long-sleeved jacket with an embellished shawl collar adorned with three novelty buttons for a classic and chic style, the modesty panel is included. The second piece is a back-slit, princess-seam skirt, the hem of which comes to mid-calf and flatters curves in a professional way.
Toss this suit in the washing machine for easy cleaning. With no need for trips to the dry cleaner, you can be ready to take charge of your workplace at a moment's notice. The hat shown on the model is sold separately. 

  Two-piece skirt suit creates a flattering yet professional  profile
  Available in red, white and chocolate for a variety of  possible combinations
  100 percent polyester and machine-washable for easy care
  Details like novelty buttons, double peplum and embellished  shawl collar add flair to a classic suit

The approximate length from the center back to the hem is Skirt: 33.5 inches. The approximate length from the jacket'stop center back to the hem is 23.5 inches. These measurements were taken from a size 10.

  Lining materials: 100-percent polyester
  Machine washable

Matched with fully lined, side zipper camisole. Finished with a skirt that is made with layered lace with satin piping, this 3-piece suit will make you look sophisticated at your next special event! Hats are sold separately.
